  "text": "Transcriptome alignment and expression estimation. Fasta files were trimmed using Flexbar 56 with settings: -adapter-min-overlap 7 -min-read-length 20 to improve read alignments. Reads were aligned by hisat2.0.5 57 using Ensembl version 74 transcripts. Reads were sorted and indexed by SAMtools 1.3.1 [CITATION_1] and then used for expression estimation by Stringtie 1.3.3 [CITATION_2] .",
